<headline>Special Weather Statement issued March 07 at 6:00PM MST  by NWS GreatFalls</headline>
<description>...Moderate to heavy snow bands expected this evening...
A period of moderate to heavy snow is expected over Fergus County
this evening. Rapid reductions in visibility to 1/4 mile or less
remain possible, along with quick freeze ups on area roadways.
Moderate to heavy snow may linger behind the initial band. Use
caution if traveling this evening and tonight.</description>
